# Task 0 - Simple Web Stack

## Infrastructure Diagram

```text
  [ User Browser ]
         │
         │ (Input: [www.foobar.com](https://www.foobar.com))
         ▼
[ DNS Lookup System ]
         │ (Finds domain -> Sends back IP 8.8.8.8)
         ▼
    [ Internet ]
         │
         ▼
┌────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
│               WEB SERVER NODE (IP: 8.8.8.8)            │
│                                                        │
│  [ Nginx Traffic Handler ]                             │
│            │                                           │
│            │ (Routes Dynamic Requests)                 │
│            ▼                                           │
│  [ Backend App Engine ] ──> Uses ──> [ Project Code ]  │
│            │                                           │
│            │ (Sends Database Queries)                  │
│            ▼                                           │
│  [ MySQL Data Storage ]                                │
└────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘
```

